---
description: Security baseline (manual use or @mention)
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

- Treat all inputs as untrusted; sanitize at boundaries.
- Secrets only in env vars; never in code.
- Cookie auth: httpOnly + SameSite; enable CSRF protection.
- Rate-limit public APIs; enforce secure headers.
- Validate file uploads (MIME/size); prefer presigned URLs.
